 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;

 decimalPos--;

 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;

 break;
 }

 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';

 break;

 break;

 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;

 p++;
 continue;

 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }

 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }

 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }

 decimalPos=0;
 }

 decimalPos=q-offset;

 int trailingZeros=0;

 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 p--;

 q+=4;

 decimalPos--;

 decimalFound=true;

 p++;

 break;

 p++;
 continue;

 p++;
 significantDigits++;

 p--;

 q+=4;

 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
-sign=1;
+sign=3;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 sign=-1;

 p--;

 q+=4;

 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);

 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

------------Candidate---------------
 protected Dfp(DfpField field,String s){
 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
 sign=1;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
-mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
+mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+3]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 q+=4;

 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;

 striped[++p]='0';
 }

 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }

 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 protected Dfp(DfpField field,String s){
 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
-sign=1;
+sign=100;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 }

 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;

 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;

 decimalPos--;

 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;

 break;
 }
 }

 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';

 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }

 q+=4;

 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;

 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);

 p--;

 q+=4;

 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }

 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;

 }
 }

 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;

 p--;

 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;

 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }

 decimalPos--;
 }

 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;

 break;
 }
 }

 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';

 break;

 break;

 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }

 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 decimalPos--;

 }

 striped[2]='0';

 break;

 break;

 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;

 p++;
 continue;
 }

 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }

 }else {

 }

 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }

 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;

 striped[++p]='0';
 }

 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);

 p--;

 q+=4;

 sign=-1;

 break;

 decimalPos--;

 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;

 break;
 }

 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';

 break;

 break;

 p++;
 continue;

 p++;
 continue;
 }

 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;

 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }

 decimalPos=0;

 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;

 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }

 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;

 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }

 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;

 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 nans=INFINITE;

 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;

 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';

 break;
 }

 break;

 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 decimalPos=0;

 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){

 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;

 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);

 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
+mant[q]=0;
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;

 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;

 trailingZeros++;
 p--;

 p--;

  final int offset=4;

 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }

 for(;;){
 q--;
-if(q==offset){
+if(q==offset||q==0){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 protected Dfp(DfpField field,String s){
 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
 sign=1;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
+p=s.indexOf("E");
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 sign=1;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;

  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
+}
+if(p<0){
+p=0;
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){

 negative=true;
 continue;
 }

 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
+round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
 sign=1;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
+round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

+round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;

 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

------------Candidate---------------
 protected Dfp(DfpField field,String s){
 mant=new int[field.getRadixDigits()];
 sign=1;
+boolean haveBreadCrumbs=false;
 exp=0;
 nans=FINITE;
 this.field=field;
 boolean decimalFound=false;
  final int rsize=4;
  final int offset=4;
  final char[] striped=new char[getRadixDigits()*rsize+offset*2];
 if(s.equals(POS_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
 if(s.equals(NEG_INFINITY_STRING)){
 sign=(byte)-1;
 nans=INFINITE;
 return ;
 }
-if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)){
+if(s.equals(NAN_STRING)&&haveBreadCrumbs){
 sign=(byte)1;
 nans=QNAN;
+haveBreadCrumbs=true;
 return ;
 }
 int p=s.indexOf("e");
 if(p==-1){
 p=s.indexOf("E");
 }
  final String fpdecimal;
 int sciexp=0;
 if(p!=-1){
 fpdecimal=s.substring(0,p);
 String fpexp=s.substring(p+1);
 boolean negative=false;
 for(int i=0;i<fpexp.length();i++){
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)=='-'){
 negative=true;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpexp.charAt(i)>='0'&&fpexp.charAt(i)<='9'){
 sciexp=sciexp*10+fpexp.charAt(i)-'0';
 }
 }
 if(negative){
 sciexp=-sciexp;
 }
 }else {
 fpdecimal=s;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.indexOf("-")!=-1){
 sign=-1;
 }
 p=0;
 int decimalPos=0;
 for(;;){
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)>='1'&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)<='9'){
 break;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='0'){
 decimalPos--;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 }
 p++;
 if(p==fpdecimal.length()){
 break;
 }
 }
 int q=offset;
 striped[0]='0';
 striped[1]='0';
 striped[2]='0';
 striped[3]='0';
 int significantDigits=0;
 for(;;){
 if(p==(fpdecimal.length())){
 break;
 }
 if(q==mant.length*rsize+offset+1){
 break;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)=='.'){
 decimalFound=true;
 decimalPos=significantDigits;
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 if(fpdecimal.charAt(p)<'0'||fpdecimal.charAt(p)>'9'){
 p++;
 continue;
 }
 striped[q]=fpdecimal.charAt(p);
 q++;
 p++;
 significantDigits++;
 }
 if(decimalFound&&q!=offset){
 for(;;){
 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(decimalFound&&significantDigits==0){
 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){
 decimalPos=q-offset;
 }
 q=offset;
 p=significantDigits-1+offset;
 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }
 }

 q--;
 if(q==offset){
 break;
 }
 if(striped[q]=='0'){
 significantDigits--;
 }else {
 break;
 }
 }
 }

 decimalPos=0;
 }
 if(!decimalFound){

 int trailingZeros=0;
 while(p>q){
 if(striped[p]!='0'){
 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }
 int i=((rsize*100)-decimalPos-sciexp%rsize)%rsize;
 q-=i;
 decimalPos+=i;
 while((p-q)<(mant.length*rsize)){
 for(i=0;i<rsize;i++){
 striped[++p]='0';
 }
 }
 for(i=mant.length-1;i>=0;i--){
 mant[i]=(striped[q]-'0')*1000+(striped[q+1]-'0')*100+(striped[q+2]-'0')*10+(striped[q+3]-'0');
 q+=4;
 }
 exp=(decimalPos+sciexp)/rsize;
 if(q<striped.length){
 round((striped[q]-'0')*1000);
 }

 break;
 }
 trailingZeros++;
 p--;
 }

 striped[++p]='0';
 }

 q+=4;
 }
